"       </td>",
"      </tr>",
"     </tbody>",
"    </table>",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    <div class=\"footnotes\">",
"     * Despite very concerning animal data, increasing human data suggests fluoroquinolones might warrant a role in specific pregnant patients in the future.",
"     <br>",
"      &bull; Only the erythromycin estolate should be avoided in pregnancy. Other forms of erythromycin, such as erythromycin base, ethyl succinate, or stearate are acceptable.",
"     </br>",
